Add migration for liveState field to media_objects table- it should use Spare3 to cause minimum disruption
Keep any live original url until the job has been archived and then convert to original ts. LiveState field is 1 whilst ingesting the live stream so that viewers can keep watching whilst it's being transcoded and then LiveState is 2 when complete
